5&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Why Ballparks Must Prioritize Safe Outfield Walls</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://ritmica1.substack.com/p/grounding-kwera?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=5688290&amp;post_id=198770035&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=false&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Grounding kwERA</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://www.mayday.show/p/why-left-handed-baseball-players?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1844059&amp;post_id=198800325&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Why left handed baseball players are weird</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://baseballspast.substack.com/p/mel-ott-and-the-polo-grounds?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=6364294&amp;post_id=198775261&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mel Ott and the Polo Grounds</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://www.wideleft.football/p/does-the-2027-nfl-draft-class-live?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1875186&amp;post_id=198057618&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Does the 2027 NFL Draft Class Live Up to the Hype?</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://gridirondeepdive.substack.com/p/who-actually-drafted-well-a-history?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1522762&amp;post_id=196679965&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Who Actually Drafted Well? A History of NFL Draft Performance</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://fancystats.substack.com/p/rest-matters-in-the-nfl-just-probably?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=7912922&amp;post_id=198407568&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rest matters in the NFL — just probably less than you think</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://club.sportico.com/p/nfl-streaming-tv-deals-fan-pushback-risk-breakdown-cost?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2699251&amp;post_id=198269418&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The NFL’s TV Talks Are Even More Perilous Than They Look</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://thespade.substack.com/p/the-tale-of-two-fourth-place-finishes?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1892935&amp;post_id=198275293&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Tale of Two Fourth Place Finishes</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://spreadsheetsandtailgates.substack.com/p/a-24-team-college-football-playoff?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=3545990&amp;post_id=173095846&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">A 24-Team College Football Playoff Solves a Problem That Doesn’t Exist</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚽ <strong><a href=\"https://bobsturm.substack.com/p/mauricio-pochettino-wont-pick-the?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=509299&amp;post_id=198629628&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mauricio Pochettino won’t pick the best 26, but he will pick the 26 he trusts</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏁 <a href=\"https://f1chronicle.substack.com/p/george-russells-championship-experience?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2611220&amp;post_id=198387922&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">George Russell’s Championship Experience Could Be Key Against Antonelli</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏁▶︎ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BCaxdsYwKaQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The chaotic rise of Kyle Busch</a></strong> by <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@NRF_Productions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NRF Productions</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>▶️ <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/my-old-games-lists\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Old YouTube RaceGame</a> of the Week</h4>\n<p>2026 NASCAR Craftsman Truck Series at Dover Motor Speedway<em> (Kyle Busch’s final win)</em></p>\n<h4>🎵 Music to Play Us Out</h4>\n<p>“Sunflower” by YOUNHA</p>\n<p><em><strong>Filed under:</strong></em> <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/t/roundup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Weekly Round-up</a></p>\n<p>Neil’s Substack is a reader-supported publication. To receive new posts and support my work, consider becoming a free or paid subscriber.</p>",
